summary:
Experienced organiser and creative problem solver. Have an eye for opportunities and business interests and apply this well to achieve good results within budget and time.

Enjoy working in a dynamic environment that pushes to draw on both analytical skills and pragmatism. Most effective when fulfilling a pivotal role that allows to engage with all stakeholders and executives involved.

Driven to gain insight, produce optimal results and to realise high quality solutions. Value strong and inspiring partnerships and always strive to create good relations with clients, suppliers and internal organization.
